  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Liferay Cloud is migrating all customer databases to MySQL 8 as MySQL 5.7 has reached its end-of-life (EoL) and will no longer receive critical updates. This upgrade ensures continued security, performance, and compatibility across all environments.</p>\n\n<p>The migration for AC-PRD has been scheduled to take place this <strong>Thursday, January 30, 2025, at 7 PM PST</strong>. The expected downtime for this migration is up to 20 minutes.</p>\n\n<p>We are committed to ensuring a smooth and seamless migration process and appreciate your patience during this critical upgrade.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
      },
